  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Welcome drink on arrival</li>
<li>Daily continental breakfast</li>
<li>Packed lunches (choose and make up your own to suit you) - 6 days per week</li>
<li>Afternoon tea with freshly baked cake - 6 days per week</li>
<li>3-course evening meal, with choice of complimentary wine, tea/coffee - 6 days per week</li>
<li>Tea and coffee is available throughout the day and fresh fruit is provided - 7 days per week</li>
</ul>
<p>For more info on chalet, Chalet Hotels and 'Half-Board Plus' arrangements <a data-udi="umb://document/ea27f8aecab440d8a3039c5e12b6284e" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ea27f8aecab440d8a3039c5e12b6284e}" title="Hotels Managed by Inghams">click here</a></p>]]></cateringDescription>
