  <description><![CDATA[<p><a data-udi="umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f5a2404579b84c448ac2a43bfaacfdd0}" title="Lech">Lech</a> is a picturesque resort and at Hotel Montfort you'll be in a quiet location, a short walk to the main streets with lots of welcoming cafés and chic shops. The nearby walkers lifts take you up to sensational scenery, with a large choice of walking trails.</p>
<p>You'll enjoy the traditional look, comfortable feel and modern facilities. The dining-room is light and airy, and the beautiful lounge/bar are typically Austrian, making a great spot to enjoy afternoon tea, pre-dinner canapés or post-dinner drinks. For a property of this size, the wellness area is a real treat. </p>
<p>Our own team of staff are very friendly. 'Half-Board PLUS' arrangement means you'll receive breakfast, dinner with wine, packed lunches, afternoon tea, and coffee all included. (provide 6 out of 7 days).</p>
<p>All bedrooms are attractive, comfortable and relaxing.</p>]]></description>
